1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 21=

21
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,680
Your Majesty.

22
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:39,310
I'm sorry for my behavior.

23
00:01:39,350 --> 00:01:40,480
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

24
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:42,400
What troubles you?

25
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:47,560
Perhaps I caught a chill last night.

26
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,400
I...

27
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:14,400
Congrats, Your Majesty.

28
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,400
Great news.

29
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,750
Concubine Hui is with child.

30
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,750
The pregnancy is stable.

31
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,270
Reward!

32
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,310
Everyone present today

33
00:02:24,370 --> 00:02:25,560
shall receive a generous reward!

34
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,840
Thank you, Your Majesty.

35
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:37,280
Go, go.

36
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:42,080
I'll issue an edict at once.

37
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,870
To confer you as Consort Hui.

38
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,280
Your Majesty.

39
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,960
Tall trees catch much wind.

40
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,400
I'm afraid

41
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:52,080
that I might end up like Consort Duan

42
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:54,400
and fail to protect this child.

43
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,840
No.

44
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,400
Don't overthink.

45
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,710
You are not like her.

46
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,590
You are the mother of my first son

47
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,960
and the only one

48
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,080
fit to be Empress in my heart.

49
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:17,280
I'll never let you or the child
come to harm.

50
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:23,190
I never dared to dream of this.

51
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:26,310
I only wish to keep the baby safe

52
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,030
and live up to your grace.

53
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,030
Congratulations, Your Ladyship.

54
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,400
I just heard

55
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,590
General Lan has quelled the rebels
in the southwest.

56
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,560
He's won another great merit.

57
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,430
General is returning to the capital.

58
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:54,190
When he's rewarded for his merit,

59
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,910
Your Ladyship will surely regain favor.

60
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,750
I've known this for a long time.

61
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,560
My brother is always brave.

62
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,840
Victory is nothing new for him.

63
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:05,190
Since Your Ladyship knew the good news,

64
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,560
you should be happy.

65
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,630
Why are you so down?

66
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:12,400
His Majesty and I
once loved each other deeply.

67
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,190
We were so devoted.

68
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,120
But now,

69
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,750
he's still angry with me

70
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,950
over Consort Duan's death.

71
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,360
I may regain his favor later,

72
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:26,800
but I'm afraid
that feeling will have faded.

73
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:29,040
I dare to speak plainly.

74
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,920
His Majesty's coldness

75
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,750
may not be because of Consort Duan.

76
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,360
What do you mean?

77
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:38,160
Consort Duan was never deeply favored.

78
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,190
The privileges she had

79
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:42,560
only came after
she carried the royal heir.

80
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:44,190
His Majesty valued her

81
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,430
not for who she was,

82
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:51,000
but for the prince in her belly.

83
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,600
His Majesty is cold by nature,

84
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:57,120
but he values imperial heirs above all.

85
00:04:57,830 --> 00:05:00,040
The harem has had no heirs for years.

86
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:01,560
The imperial bloodline is thin.

87
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,190
Exactly so.

88
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:07,190
Your Ladyship, you and His Majesty
once loved each other..

89
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:09,390
If you have a child now,

90
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,120
His Majesty will fall for you again

91
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,720
and rekindle your love.

92
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,190
It's not that easy.

93
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,430
I've been favored for years,

94
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,600
but never conceived.

95
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:23,720
I've seen all imperial
and folk physicians.

96
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,870
They all said I'm healthy.

97
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,950
But I just

98
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,560
can't get pregnant.

99
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,240
What?

100
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:41,000
Concubine Hui is pregnant?

101
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,430
Yesterday, His Majesty suddenly

102
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:46,430
gave two of his chief eunuchs

103
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,630
to Concubine Hui.

104
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,430
And just now, the Empress Dowager

105
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:52,360
sent two loyal senior nannies

106
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,600
to Concubine Hui's Palace.

107
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,600
So the news must be true.

108
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:02,040
She's just a selected woman
who's been here less than a year

109
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,600
with a humble background.

110
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,310
What makes her so special?

111
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,750
His Majesty never cared for
Consort Duan this much.

112
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:14,560
Now he's protecting her
like she's in mortal danger.

113
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,920
Who is he guarding against?

114
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,040
Me?

115
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,240
Calm down, Your Ladyship.

116
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:23,310
Consort Duan came from a noble family.

117
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:26,040
The Empress Dowager
couldn't interfere with her staff.

118
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,160
But Concubine Hui is ordinary.

119
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,240
So

120
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,950
His Majesty and the Empress Dowager
can easily arrange her staff.

121
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:34,190
That's why they replaced her servants.

122
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,600
It's not special favor.

123
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,070
She just

124
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,360
got lucky.

125
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,270
Yes.

126
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,830
Your Ladyship, don't let it rile you.

127
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,750
She's just pregnant.

128
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:47,310
The days ahead are still long.

129
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,080
Stop.

130
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,310
Consort De didn't summon you.

131
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,190
Why bring a food box here?

132
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,830
I made new pastries today.

133
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,600
I know Consort De loves sweet things,

134
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,000
so I brought them for her.

135
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:09,430
You can't see Consort De
whenever you want.

136
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:12,830
But only Consort De can decide that.

137
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:15,600
Please tell her for me.

138
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,120
You want us to pass word for you?

139
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,310
As long as we're here,

140
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,390
you'll never step foot in here.

141
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,360
Well, you two

142
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,080
are mean

143
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:34,230
and stupid.

144
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,800
Someone played you,

145
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,800
yet you don't see
your days are numbered.

146
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:41,000
If I were you two,

147
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,720
I'd find an excuse to leave here.

148
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,830
It might save your lives.

149
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:46,790
You...

150
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,040
How dare you curse us!

151
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,720
Miss Ye Jin, you're here.

152
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,000
Chuntao.

153
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,850
Perfect timing.

154
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:53,480
Consort De was just speaking of you.

155
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:54,590
Please, come in.

156
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,440
Move aside.

157
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,040
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

158
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,750
I heard you brought pastries.

159
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,200
Well?

160
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,950
Aren't you afraid
I'll make things hard for you?

161
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,750
These pastries are more than food today.

162
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,600
They're medicine

163
00:08:26,810 --> 00:08:28,360
to cure your heartache.

164
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,600
Heartache?

165
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:32,750
What heartache do I have?

166
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,910
This pastry is called

167
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,510
Future.

168
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:42,910
Would Your Ladyship be interested

169
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,030
in how it's made?

170
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:47,200
Interesting.

171
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:51,440
A lowly maid dares to
teach me about my future?

172
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,510
Your Ladyship.

173
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,360
You are beautiful

174
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,240
from a great family

175
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:59,360
and you disdain harem rivalries.

176
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:02,030
I truly admire your nobility.

177
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:03,960
But it's not
how to survive in the harem.

178
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,150
You must know about

179
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,240
the rumors a few days ago.

180
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,750
If the Empress Dowager
hadn't acted firmly,

181
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:13,600
you and your family's reputation

182
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,510
would have been trampled into the dirt.

183
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,550
Then what do you think I should do?

184
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,720
If Your Ladyship
wants peace in the harem,

185
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,390
you need status and power.

186
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:28,550
And only His Majesty can give you those.

187
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,440
You don't have to always
share his bed to win his favor.

188
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:36,030
If Your Ladyship uses your strengths,

189
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:39,550
there may be another way.

190
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,750
My strengths?

191
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:52,870
Your Majesty.

192
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:55,790
Concubine De, you're here today.

193
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,120
Is there something urgent?

194
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,270
I'd like you to taste some dishes.

195
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,680
Taste dishes?

196
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,720
You know me, Your Majesty.

197
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,200
I love food

198
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,320
and I love creating pastries and dishes.

199
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,600
Since I entered the palace
to serve Your Majesty,

200
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,390
I've wanted to make new dishes

201
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,960
to suit your taste.

202
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,000
I've studied for a long time

203
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,840
and I've finally made some progress.

204
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,200
So I invited you today

205
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,960
to my palace to taste them.

206
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,600
You've put so much thought into this.

207
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:24,670
I entered the palace to serve you,
Your Majesty.

208
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:31,230
Let's go.

209
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,510
I'm just hungry.

210
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,720
Eunuch Sixi just sent someone over

211
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,600
to inform

212
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:50,750
that His Majesty
won't come for breakfast today.

213
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,750
He's gone to Concubine De's palace.

214
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:55,840
I know.

215
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,800
What's wrong?

216
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:04,760
Your Ladyship.

217
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,600
I heard it was Ye Jin's idea

218
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:11,600
to have Concubine De
win His Majesty's favor with food.

219
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:14,320
We thought she was one of us.

220
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:17,120
Who knew she's turned to Concubine De

221
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:19,030
for power.

222
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:20,630
Where did you

223
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,240
hear this?

224
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,120
A fellow maid from my hometown

225
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,840
works as a cleaner
in Concubine De's palace.

226
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:28,120
She told me.

227
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:29,840
She's honest and reliable.

228
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,240
So she'd never lie.

229
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,840
Ye Jin has indeed been

230
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,320
very close with Concubine De.

231
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,240
I believe Ye Jin would never betray me.

232
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,750
Don't say

233
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,240
these words again.

234
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,630
Yes.

235
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,840
Your Majesty,

236
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,240
this is the new tea of the year.

237
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,560
New tea?

238
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,960
Let me have a taste.

239
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,840
Not bad.

240
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:00,200
Greetings, mother.

241
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:02,440
Mother, how have you been lately?

242
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,200
Thanks to your brother,

243
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,750
I'm well.

244
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,840
Did you just leave court?

245
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,840
Why aren't you in the Imperial Study
reading edicts,

246
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:14,440
instead of visiting me?

247
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,680
I...

248
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:18,750
want your advice.

249
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:22,840
You've ruled for years.

250
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,910
What matter

251
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:26,000
still needs my advice?

252
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,840
I...

253
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,440
want to promote Concubine De
to Consort De.

254
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,320
But she hasn't been in the palace long.

255
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,600
Promoting her too soon

256
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,490
may be inappropriate.

257
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,600
I've thought it over,

258
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,600
and I think it's proper to ask

259
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,440
for your advice first.

260
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,240
You never liked Concubine De before.

261
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,390
Why the change of heart?

262
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,240
I have no love for her.

263
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,600
But she's smart, decisive,
and knows her place.

264
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,630
She's someone I can use.

265
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,440
The harem has no virtuous leader.

266
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,000
No one can rule alone.

267
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,200
Concubine Hui and her child

268
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,030
must not meet Consort Duan's fate.

269
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:05,930
Yes.

270
00:13:06,060 --> 00:13:08,550
Actually, letting Concubine De
enter the palace back then

271
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:10,440
was also to keep Consort Lan in check.

272
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,550
Now that she understands,

273
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:14,390
I'm glad to see it through.

274
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,080
So I'm willing to give her the honor.

275
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:20,600
But General Lan will return soon.

276
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,960
He is a great meritorious man.

277
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,000
Consort Lan's confinement

278
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,000
should be lifted.

279
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:30,590
I

280
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,910
had the same thought.

281
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:43,080
By the Emperor's divine order,

282
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:45,030
Concubine De of the Tongjia Clan.

283
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,600
Upon entering the palace,

284
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,240
you followed the late Emperor's will.

285
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,910
You mastered ritual,

286
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:51,670
never slacked in duty,

287
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,200
showed grace with restraint,

288
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,720
and holds a gentle heart.

289
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:57,150
I hereby promote Concubine De
to Consort De.

290
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,200
By Imperial Decree.

291
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:16,670
Congratulations, Consort De.

292
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,840
Congratulations, Your Ladyship.

293
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:29,900
(Consort De of the Tongjia Clan)

294
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:43,240
Congratulations, Consort De.

295
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,320
Your wish has come true.

296
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:46,240
Rise.

297
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,720
Thank you, Consort De.

298
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,360
This is all thanks to you.

299
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,840
If you hadn't given me the idea,

300
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:56,630
I never would've known I could win favor

301
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,840
without sharing his bed

302
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:02,390
or flattering him, just with a meal.

303
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,120
If word got out,

304
00:15:04,690 --> 00:15:05,840
I doubt anyone would believe it.

305
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,750
Everything happens for a reason.

306
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,510
His Majesty needs you.

307
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:13,030
You've been scheming to help me.

308
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,120
What are you after?

309
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,750
We still

310
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:19,150
have an old score to settle.

311
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,320
Your Ladyship,

312
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:22,840
I never saw you as an enemy.

313
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:24,320
In my eyes,

314
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,600
you are just

315
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,440
a woman who loves deeply.

316
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,330
On the contrary,

317
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:30,840
I admire your courage to love and hate.

318
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,510
Admire me?

319
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,750
You stole the one I love.

320
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,910
And now you say you admire me?

321
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,240
You're quite the talker.

322
00:15:40,510 --> 00:15:41,840
Since you entered the palace,

323
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,630
you carry your family's hopes.

324
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:46,550
Being a Noble Consort is glory now,

325
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,720
but the palace is full of danger.

326
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:51,200
The harem isn't a battlefield,
but it's just as brutal.

327
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,720
Enemies all around you,

328
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,720
trouble within and beyond.

329
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,510
So there's no need to
waste your thoughts

330
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:57,960
on someone as lowly as me.

331
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:01,320
Besides, I'm your helper,

332
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,550
not your hindrance.

333
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,030
You're no ordinary maid.

334
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,750
Losing to you

335
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,240
is not a disgrace.

336
00:16:14,650 --> 00:16:15,750
How beautiful these flowers are.

337
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:16,590
Look at that one.

338
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:18,120
This one is lovely too.

339
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,440
Isn't it?

340
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,240
Greetings, Consort De.

341
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,390
Please rise.

342
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,150
We are all family.

343
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:27,150
No need for formalities.

344
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:28,910
The sun is perfect today.

345
00:16:28,910 --> 00:16:30,030
And the flowers are in full bloom.

346
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,320
Since everyone is here,

347
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,840
let's enjoy the spring scenery together.

348
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,750
We'd love to.

349
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:38,240
It's an honor to be with you.

350
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,870
She has only been
in the palace a short while,

351
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,840
and now she's a Noble Consort.

352
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:51,360
But she'll never surpass Your Ladyship.

353
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:54,000
Consort Duan was also a Noble Consort.

354
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,510
And she outranked me just
by bearing a royal heir.

355
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,600
Now this Consort De

356
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:00,840
is young,

357
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,030
from a fine family,

358
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,960
even fairer than Consort Duan,

359
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:07,550
and a hundred times smarter.

360
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:11,240
If she has a prince,

361
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:14,160
how can I win?

362
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:15,830
Don't lose hope, Your Ladyship.

363
00:17:15,830 --> 00:17:17,590
General will be back soon.

364
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:18,830
He dotes on Your Ladyship the most.

365
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:20,510
He'll surely find a way
for Your Ladyship.

366
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:23,350
His Majesty is unhappy
with my brother lately.

367
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,000
Why drag my brother

368
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:27,400
into harem affairs?

369
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,920
I have a series of plans.

370
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,400
They can help Your Ladyship

371
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,350
turn the tables.

372
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:41,700
♪I am but an outsider♪

373
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:43,900
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

374
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:48,180
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

375
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:52,420
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

376
00:17:56,700 --> 00:17:59,940
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

377
00:18:00,100 --> 00:18:03,500
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

378
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:06,020
♪I know how this story ends♪

379
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:10,580
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

380
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:15,020
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

381
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:23,300
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

382
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:26,580
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

383
00:18:26,780 --> 00:18:29,860
♪A history that no one can search♪

384
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:33,380
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

385
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:35,180
♪I am but an outsider♪

386
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:37,420
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

387
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:41,460
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

388
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:46,140
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

389
00:18:50,060 --> 00:18:53,460
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

390
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:56,820
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

391
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:59,300
♪I know how this story ends♪

392
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:03,460
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

393
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:06,740
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

394
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:10,540
♪Please forget me and move on♪

395
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:16,780
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

396
00:19:19,940 --> 00:19:28,300
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

397
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:41,580
♪When do I finally wake♪
